                            <comment id="14454094" author="dfabulich" created="Fri, 23 Nov 2007 10:05:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in revision 597693.  I never could reproduce any problem with this behavior on my Windows machine, but doing this the right way is easy and doesn&apos;t seem to hurt anything.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454180" author="david@davidkarlsen.com" created="Fri, 4 Jan 2008 06:07:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Try &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.davidkarlsen.com/avesvn/aspects/trunk/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.davidkarlsen.com/avesvn/aspects/trunk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
run&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mvn -Pltw clean test &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mvn -Pctw clean test&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;*NIX &lt;br/&gt;
both succeed on a windows machine - and bot will fail on a *NIX box.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
